breakpoints means break a screen content.
other word, it means set responsive website.

size 
(1) mobile device       (extra small screen)               max-width : 576px
(2) max mobile device   (small screen)                     min-width : 576px 
(3) tablet device       (medium screen)                    min-width : 768px
(4) mini leptop screen  (large screen)                     min-width : 992px
(5) medium leptop screen  (extra large)                    min-width : 1200px 
(6) tv screen           (extra extra large)                min-width : 1400px

max = means one type of range 
min = out of range 